软件包 com.star.reportng

类摘要
AbstractReporter Convenient base class for the ReportNG reporters.
AbstractReporter.EmptyDirectoryFilter  
HTMLReporter Enhanced HTML reporter for TestNG that uses Velocity templates to generate its output.
JUnitXMLReporter JUnit XML reporter for TestNG that uses Velocity templates to generate its output.
JUnitXMLReporter.TestClassResults Groups together all of the data about the tests results from the methods of a single test class.
ReportMetadata  
ReportNGUtils Utility class that provides various helper methods that can be invoked from a Velocity template.
TestClassComparator Comparator for sorting classes alphabetically by fully-qualified name.
TestMethodComparator Comparator for sorting TestNG test methods.
TestResultComparator Comparator for sorting TestNG test results alphabetically by method name.
 

异常摘要
ReportNGException Unchecked exception thrown when an unrecoverable error occurs during report generation.
